title: It’s not too late: Plenty of hot-ticket items are still up for grabs from Target's 20th Anniversary Collection
text:
The editors at Yahoo Lifestyle are committed to finding you the best products at the best prices. At times, we may receive a share from purchases made via links on this page.

View photos Target’s 20th Anniversary collection is selling like hotcakes, so act fast! More

Not surprisingly, pieces at Target’s 20th Anniversary Sale (featuring items from iconic brands like Marimekko, Lilly Pulitzer and Isaac Mizrahi) are selling like hotcakes. But lots of amazing stuff is still available—from clothing to housewares. We’ve picked our favorite things that are still in stock. Get them while you can!

Leopard Print Drawstring Carryall Bag - 3.1 Phillip Lim for Target (Photo: Target) More

The perfect bag for a weekend away, with a drawstring closure and interior zippered pockets. Go wild!

Shop it: Leopard Print Drawstring Carryall Bag - 3.1 Phillip Lim for Target, $40, target.com

Women's Sleeveless Slip Mini Dress - Rodarte for Target (Photo: Target) More

Rock your next cocktail party with this cool mustard yellow dress with a tulle overlay, lace detailing and bow accents.

Shop it: Women’s Sleeveless Slip Mini Dress - Rodarte for Target Mustard Yellow, $40, target.com

Women's Floral Print Long Sleeve V-Neck Maxi Dress - Altuzarra for Target (Photo: Target) More

Bring on the drama with this floral number featuring a thigh-high slit. Oooh! The maxi style and long sleeves are ideal for winter.

Shop it: Women's Floral Print Long Sleeve V-Neck Maxi Dress - Altuzarra for Target, $35, target.com
description: From Missoni bags to Marimekko chairs, some of the best items are still in stock—but hurry!
